name: Your Game
description:
Your Game is a small example of what can be achieved with an asset pack i've made available on itch.io
Download the game, have a look.
I'm looking forward to seeing what you make with these models. The possibilities are endless.

If you would like to expand on this game, all the asset files are available here:

https://phrygian100.itch.io/3d-models-modular-domestic-environment
